data.description: Welcome to your tranquil oasis! This immaculate, like-new manufactured home, nestled on just over an acre of land, offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and peaceful country living. With only two years of age, this property boasts all the benefits of a brand-new home without the wait or hassle. Get ready to experience the serenity and quietude that can only be found in this beautiful corner of the world.
